<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-mismasFraccionesDiferenteResultado" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample response: Lin got a different answer than Han because her number lines are not the same length. Because she drew one number line longer than the other, it makes it look like <m>\frac{4}{6}</m> is greater than <m>\frac{5}{6}</m>.</p>
  </solution>


